
JRuby SWT Cookbook
==================

JRuby and SWT is a great platform for writing cross-platform desktop applications. This repo contains 
examples of how to get started.

Getting Started
---------------

  1. You will need to run these examples with JRuby. Get it from jruby.org.
  2. You need the correct SWT jar for your platform. Get it from www.eclipse.org/swt. 
     Take the file called `swt.jar` from the download and put it in the root of this 
     directory.

